snippet.title: Michael Jackson Secures Massive Win! Judge Denies Liar Wade Robson Lawsuit
snippet.description:
With #MJInnocent Trending, I wanted to add my voice to the movement. I'm so disgusted by the media's portrayal of Michael Jackson after his death... And the world's acceptance of a biased hit piece documentary as facts of guilt. Do the homework... Then realize these people only came forward after Michael Jackson's death, when he couldn't defend himself. It's not right. So its good to hear the Jackson Estate get a win like this.

Learn more about the truth about Michael Jackson, in my interviews with Taj Jackson over on Hugging The Cactus - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G0Bc3WPcxwM
